{"tid":1660791,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工除咗可以令自己搵多啲錢捐比義士之外好似一啲意義都冇","createTime":"2019-10-17T17:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T15:08:11.000Z","uid":79927,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"980483f5f2fc3c2a0809b31f63f5e17b62e6662d","tid":1660791,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"一返full time，就算份工再hea, 一星期都起馬有五日時間個人要stay係公司八個鐘<br />\n更何況好多冇乜時間hea，唔少仲要ot<br />\n如果對自己的做緊嘅野有興趣有熱情都還好<br />\n我自己就對自己的嘅工作一啲興趣都冇，其實可以話幾厭惡<br />\n但我另一方面又諗唔到做咩工自己係會鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好大機會返咩工都咁厭惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗深一層，自己都冇需要返一份full time工<br />\n平日好毒，冇女冇社交冇娛樂<br />\n亦都冇乜物慾，除咗食飯搭車每個月最大嘅消費就係gym room月費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近依幾個月又同屋企啲廢老反埋面，錢都唔洗點比佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個月都係用四五千蚊左右，跟住剩低嘅錢就一部份捐比義士<br />\n一部份儲落黎，但錢都唔係一定要儲，因為我自己對人生都冇咩好長遠嘅規劃，又冇乜特別想做嘅野需要用錢去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果辭咗份full time, 一個禮拜搵兩日去炒下散<br />\n都夠我過日子有突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一壞處就係令我唔會再有多餘嘅錢捐比義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7fdc39d5a01acd3454b4203d847abdc4e19378","tid":1660791,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢都無過多嘅娛樂<br />\n我都有課金<br />\n啲錢用得好有意義"},{"pid":"8030efbc17acfc2a7b76d85689f609324ba9bf85","tid":1660791,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"F<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AQTzVBz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQTzVBz.jpg&h=071a7779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HULFQ9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHULFQ9U.jpg&h=f1ed96fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"483f8d03dcc7de79d8239d95374f4d0022e7fd12","tid":1660791,"uid":34116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:54:56.000Z","msg":"代義士多謝巴打你捐錢"},{"pid":"8dfba62ad5b5fa1de5665792e7dcd247363da7a7","tid":1660791,"uid":195252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"這就是光復香港的原因"},{"pid":"6b1ae12ecbef1d2a9209a187ee2c1d4656c7e425","tid":1660791,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"同樓主有d似，但我宜家無工返，又唔知做咩工先有興趣，是但搵份又怕太悶會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335087269b148feddab14e15b0ce220f0d4f54bb","tid":1660791,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"仲有 撳曬出嚟換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212c4e73a63474a9aad8522e1fbb02916e0487ad","tid":1660791,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b1ae12ecbef1d2a9209a187ee2c1d4656c7e425","tid":1660791,"uid":192242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"同樓主有d似，但我宜家無工返，又唔知做咩工先有興趣，是但搵份又怕太悶會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:49:32.000Z","msg":"搵咗幾年都未搵到自己嘅興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f7a8d2997c34273a9a235df7b5bb60ec4d1096","tid":1660791,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"335087269b148feddab14e15b0ce220f0d4f54bb","tid":1660791,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"仲有 撳曬出嚟換美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172fd0a4aa0a4635fb48a2d5f6ddf