要！"},{"pid":"4787eba60e11373e2e8db868659324c75b9d4d32","tid":1660791,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<del>返工</del>人生除咗可以令自己搵多啲錢捐比義士之外好似一啲意義都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3506b0be569ed9a365b81e12e22bc6bca9fd4f","tid":1660791,"uid":34787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"畢竟係長期抗爭，搵錢去捐，懲罰黃店係主要目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}